Rosuvastatin is also a unique member of the class of statins due to its high hydrophilicity which increases hepatic uptake at the site of action, low bioavailability, and minimal metabolism via the Cytochrome P450 system.[A181523] This last point results in less risk of drug-drug interactions compared to [atorvastatin], [lovastatin], and [simvastatin], which are all extensively metabolized by Cytochrome P450 (CYP) 3A4, an enzyme involved in the metabolism of many commonly used drugs.[A181460] Drugs such as [ciclosporin], [gemfibrozil], and some antiretrovirals are more likely to interact with this statin through antagonism of OATP1B1 organic anion transporter protein 1B1-mediated hepatic uptake of rosuvastatin.[F4649, F4652]','["C10BX10", "C10BX05", "C10BX07", "C10AA07", "A10BH52", "G01AE10", "C10BX13", "C10BX09", "C10BA09", "C10BX16", "C10BX17", "C10BX14", "C10BA06"]','[]'),(16906,'C-retard + zinc 20 caps.','سي ريتارد+زنك 20 كبسولة','80','60','Multivitamin','Vitamin c+zinc','Hikma pharma','Cap','كبسولة','','2','','for enhancing the immune system and prophylactic prevention of infection. 500 mg vitamin c + 5 mg zinc','6221000005817','',2969,'2024-12-26',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(16908,'Thymorayzen mouth spray50 ml','ثيمورايزن سبراي للفم 50 مل','70','63','Antibacterial antiulcer antiviral antifungal mouth spray','Thyme extract + guava leaf extract + salvia officinalis + zingeber officinalis + hyaluronic acid + clove oil + sodiumcholoride + clove oil + vitamin c + tee tree oil + sodium benzoate + echinacea extract','Medrayzen pharma','Spray','بخاخ','50 ml','1','سبرا للفم منعش ومطهر ومضاد لالتهابات الحلق واللثة ومخفف للالام ويساعد فى الحماية من التسوس','','','',1194,'2025-11-02',0,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL),(16910,'Cripple-d cream 50 gm','كريبل د كريم 50 جم','25','','Diaper rash','Zinc oxide+aloe vera+chamomile+panthenol+olive oil+propolis','Cosmopack for cosmetics > m.n.b','Cream','كريم','50 gm','1','','for diaper rash','','',761,'202